title: Home - Children In Adversity
og_title: Advancing Protection and Care for Children in Adversity
og_description: The United States Government envisions a world in which all children thrive within protective, loving families, free from deprivation, violence and danger. Advancing Protection and Care for Children in Adversity: A U.S. Government Strategy for International Assistance outlines the U.S. Government’s whole-of-government commitment and approach to investing in the development, care, dignity, and safety of the world’s most-vulnerable children and their families for the next five years.
